impl Cache<(usize, usize), CachedPage>

Source

pub fn get_page( &self, device: &Weak<dyn CachedAccess>, offset: usize, ) -> CacheArc<CacheItem<(usize, usize), CachedPage>>

Returns the cached page at the given offset, if not present, it will be allocated, initialized with the data on the disk and placed in the page cache.

§Arguments
  • device - The device to get the page from.
  • offset - The offset in bytes to the data. This will be rounded down to the nearest page boundary.
